      <ph props="autonumber">5613.500</ph> General.</title>
   <conbody>
      <p id="RbwLSt">(a)</p>
      <p id="fXzglC" outputclass="List3">(i) Solicitations and awards shall be reviewed and approved in accordance with <xref format="docx" href="https://sof.atl.socom.mil/sites/K/SOFARS_DCG/SOFARS/Attachment_5601-1.docx" scope="external">
            <u>Attachment 5601-1</u>
         </xref>.</p>
      <p id="gEtXsO" outputclass="List3">
         <ph>(ii)</ph>
         <xref format="html" href="https://sof.socom.mil/sites/SORDAC/K/SCN201003/SOFARS/Attachment_5601-1.htm" scope="external">
            <u>Contracting officers with a Simplified Acquisition Threshold warrant cannot sign awards made in accordance with the authority of this paragraph.</u>
         </xref>
      </p>
